reviewText: Ok, its a funny title and at first you laugh because it just seems different and easy. But five to ten minutes in it kicks your butt. I am only 28, i don't work out much and i find that the other videos are to fast or complicated right now to do. This video is a great beginners video for working out. I am already seeing a difference in energy and have lost weight. Its just a practical work out plan, which reminds me of gym class in school.
